txt.en: 'Stealth may be our only option at the moment. The gate is barred and heavily guarded, and did you see the archers who patrol the walls? Luck would have it that the orkish assault which invaded Cair Andros also left gaps in the walls which guard the island. We must sneak around the entrance, enter the fortress and defeat the archers which patrol the walls.'
Leading a band of Gondorians, Duinhir, lord of Blackroot Vale, has been tasked with the retaking of Cair Andros.
Defeat Orc scouts on the fortress walls around Cair Andros.
You have defeated many Orc scouts upon the walls of Cair Andros and have weakened the Enemy foothold on the island fortress.
